<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. A lungkhamna mun thil hitiu,
 Lalpa a mat nau chu;
 Gethsemani huon sung achun,
 A ul thisan a luong.

[V2]
 2. Simon Barjon, na chemzam in,
 Dal zolo ding na him?
 Ka Hukdampa a chiehpih tau,
 Thiempu lal Insung ah.

[V3]
 3. Linglukhuk le lal puon a pieu,
 Mawlh in chibai a pieu;
 &quot;Kuo ahim a hun khen gen in,
 Ti'n Amah a dawng ui.

[V4]
 4. Aw ei Tanpa a na taluoi,
 Kei dinga Na thawkna!
 Giloten le a khu ngei puou,
 Na linglukhuk bang hi.</lyrics>
<title>Lalpa Lungkhamna</title>
<hymn_number>58</hymn_number>
<author>Taivela</author>
</song>